      "writtenOn": "2026-03-12T13:24:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e Which is not allowed in redfish from my understanding.\n\nCan you quote the spec here ? \nI don\u0027t read below to mean you can\u0027t do this: \n\"\u0027The service root and resource path component parts uniquely identify the resource in a Redfish service.`.\"",
      "parentUuid": "9d8e9bc4_9a21bbc8",
      "range": {
